overview: "SeDUCKtion" documents a failed attempt by Gibbens to attract some ducks by a pond using a speculum with lipstick as a beak, washing-up gloves as webbed feet and a repetitive dance. Onlookers are confused. In the voice-over, a child reads online discussions comparing the sexiness of Daisy Duck and Minnie Mouse.
title: SeDUCKtion
